thread.title: Maggie

author: Maggie
title: Maggie
text: My first time buying from Willisorchard. I order almost 30 plants they came two months later only two boxes. My husband open and we see just trees with roots no leaves we looking at each other and I said they look dead. Of course we unwrap them and planted them two week later. About 4weeks later we see leaves popping out and even some come out with flowers I can't believe it.!! ALL of the plants made IT!!! I thought surely half of them would not survived . We was thrilled!!!.. Thanks You ...
